title: The Concubine’s Daughter Comes Around - Novel Updates
tags: Alternate World   Ancient Times   Black Belly   Cold Protagonist   Complex Family Relationships   Doting Love Interests   Female Protagonist   Overpowered Protagonist   Protagonist Strong from the Start   Rebellion   Siblings   Strong Love Interests   Strong to Stronger   Transmigration
author: Fei na   肥娜
description:
After reviving unexpectedly, the concubine’s daughter was no longer a coward like before, but a hard nut.

Flamed her up and bullied her?

Come on!

She came from the 21st century! How could she willingly embrace such destiny?

“Since you ask for it, see how I will torture you!”

She punished the scums and struggled against bad minions!

See how the concubine’s daughter Dong Ling would stand up and master her own fate!>
